{"type": "entity", "name": "Meta-Mind Task Progression Issues", "entityType": "WorkflowLearning", "observations": ["Observed `meta-mind` failing to automatically update task statuses.", "Workaround: Manual `update_todo_list` calls after each step.", "Learning: Emphasizes explicit state management in automated workflows.", "Methodology learnings: Explicit state management via update_todo_list after steps.", "Observed failures in automatic task status updates; workaround with manual tracking.", "Timestamp: 2025-09-30", "Reusability: 80% (tool coordination)", "last_updated: 2025-09-30", "Methodology: Iterative validation with read_graph post-changes to confirm no orphans.", "Condensed: Manual update_todo_list workaround for meta-mind status failures (62 chars). Reusability: 80%.", "obs_check_date: 2025-10-02, hash: SHA-256(Meta-Mind Task Progression Issues), reference_count: 4", "last_updated: 2025-09-30, reference_count: 4, hash: SHA256(SHA-256(Meta-Mind Task Progression Issues), obsolete_check_da"]}
