{"type": "entity", "name": "Global.Workflow.Memory.MemoryOptimizationCrossProjectPromotion_Workflow", "entityType": "Workflow", "observations": ["Purpose: Systematic memory optimization, knowledge condensation,+cross-project pattern promotion for enhanced MCP ecosys", "Workflow Steps: MEMORY_ASSESSMENT, CONDENSATION_ANALYSIS, OPTIMIZATION_EXECUTION, VALIDATION_ASSESSMENT", "MEMORY_ASSESSMENT Actions: Memory Scan, Pattern Detection, Redundancy Analysis, Connection Mapping, Quality Assessment, ", "MEMORY_ASSESSMENT Outputs: Memory structure analysis, Redundancy report, Cross-project promotion candidates", "CONDENSATION_ANALYSIS Actions: Density Calc, Abstraction Map, Consolidation Plan, Elimination Target, Pattern Extract, U", "CONDENSATION_ANALYSIS Outputs: Density analysis, Pattern abstraction map, Consolidation + elimination plan", "OPTIMIZATION_EXECUTION Actions: Memory Consolidation, Domain Structure, Global Promotion (Architectural, Implementation,", "OPTIMIZATION_EXECUTION Outputs: Consolidated memory, Promoted global patterns, Zero orphaned entities", "VALIDATION_ASSESSMENT Actions: Improvement Metrics, Domain Validation, Retrieval Testing, Cross-Project Impact (Reusabil", "VALIDATION_ASSESSMENT Outputs: Validation report, Cross-project impact assessment, Strategy documentation", "Success Targets: Connectivity (100% connected entities), Memory Efficiency (15-30% size reduction, 100% knowledge preser", "Parameters: Memory scope, Aggressiveness, Target reduction, Promotion criteria, Cross-project applicability, Global inte", "Output Format: MEMORY_AREA, ACTION, CURRENT, PROPOSED, RATIONALE, REUSABILITY, GLOBAL_INTEGRATION, IMPACT, PRIORITY", "MCP Ecosystem Integration: Dual Memory Architecture, Pattern Abstraction, Cross-Project Learning, Knowledge Bridges, Eco", "New test suite implemented in `tests/memory_optimization/test_memory_workflow.py`.", "Tests cover connectivity, memory efficiency, domain organization, retrieval performance, and cross-project impact.", "Documentation for the test suite created in `docs/technical/memory_optimization_tests.md`.", "Learnings from ANALYZE phase: Global memory redundancy identified and addressed, new promotion candidates created.", "Learnings from EXECUTE phase: Memory consolidation, pattern promotion,+knowledge bridge creation completed. Observed dis", "Learnings from TEST phase: New tests created to validate memory optimization, knowledge graph integrity, domain organiza", "Documentation Plan: New architectural document for the workflow under `docs/arch/memory_optimization_workflow.md` (or `d", "Documentation Plan: Update `docs/technical/memory_optimization_tests.md` w/test suite overview, validation results,+test", "Verification Plan: Manual review of updated documentation, cross-reference w/global memory entity, verification of succe", "Systematic workflow for memory optimization, knowledge condensation,+cross-project pattern promotion. Encompasses assess", "Learnings from ANALYZE phase (Phase 3 - Domain Layer Analysis): Identified a generic, unassigned cluster ('Project.Clust", "Phase 12 (Type Layer Analysis) completed. Generated analysis report: logs/memory_analysis_global_2025-09-27_172828.md. I", "Documentation for the 'Update Memory Workflow' created at `docs/architecture/memory_optimization_report.md`.", "last_updated: 2025-10-08, reference_count: 0, hash: SHA256(207cc97f23cfe0f1), obsolete_check_date: 2025-10-08"]}
