{"type": "entity", "name": "Global.Phase9.EntityLayerAnalysis_Report", "entityType": "AnalysisReport", "observations": ["Phase 9 Summary: Analyzed 80 entities; 16 disconnected (20%), 65/80 (81%) universal (≥80% reusability); Metadata: 70% co", "Disconnected Entities (16): Global.UIPattern.Input.CommandInputAutoUpdate_Pattern (no UI domain), Global.PythonClass.Pre", "Universal Patterns (65): Examples - CircuitBreaker_Pattern (90%, distributed resilience), ServiceLayer_Pattern (88%, MVC", "Metadata Gaps (10): Missing last_updated/reusability/entityType (e.g., GlobalSnapshot_20250808, Workflow Finalization). ", "Obsoletes (4): Global.System.Snapshot.GlobalSnapshot_20250808 (>180d, 0 refs, outdated), Global.Snapshot.Archive.2025080", "Condensations (8 merges): ErrorHandling variants → Delegation_Pattern (save 3), UI dynamic → Unified_Pattern (save 2), B", "obs_check_date: 2025-10-02, hash: SHA-256 of report content, reference_count: 80 entities analyzed", "last_updated: 2025-10-08, reference_count: 80, hash: SHA256(SHA-256 of report content, reference_count: 80 entities anal"]}
